[6] Write HTML program to create a webpage for a fictional event called "I2IT TechCon
2025." This webpage will include
● A header introducing the event.
● Navigation links for different sections (About, Schedule, Contact).
● A schedule table.
● A contact form

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>I2IT TechCon 2025</title>

    <style>

        body
        {
            font-family: Arial;
            margin: 0;
            background-color: #f2f2f2;
        }

        /* Header */

        .header
        {
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        /* Navigation Bar */

        .navbar
        {
            background-color: black;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .navbar a
        {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin: 15px;
            font-size: 18px;
        }

        /* Section */

        .container
        {
            width: 80%;
            margin: auto;
            background-color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }

        /* Table */

        table
        {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 15px;
        }

        table, th, td
        {
            border: 1px solid black;
        }

        th
        {
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        td
        {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 10px;
        }

        /* Form */

        input, textarea
        {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 8px;
            margin-top: 5px;
        }

        .btn
        {
            background-color: darkblue;
            color: white;
            border: none;
        }

    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <!-- Header -->

    <div class="header">

        <h1>I2IT TechCon 2025</h1>

        <p>Technology Conference for Innovation and Learning</p>

    </div>

    <!-- Navigation -->

    <div class="navbar">

        <a href="#about">About</a>

        <a href="#schedule">Schedule</a>

        <a href="#contact">Contact</a>

    </div>

    <!-- About Section -->

    <div class="container" id="about">

        <h2><u>About Event</u></h2>

        <p>
            I2IT TechCon 2025 is a fictional technology event organized for students
            to explore new trends in Web Development, AI, Cloud Computing, and Cyber Security.
        </p>

    </div>

    <!-- Schedule Section -->

    <div class="container" id="schedule">

        <h2><u>Event Schedule</u></h2>

        <table>

            <tr>
                <th>Time</th>
                <th>Session</th>
                <th>Speaker</th>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>10:00 AM</td>
                <td>Web Development</td>
                <td>Mr. Rahul Sharma</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>12:00 PM</td>
                <td>Artificial Intelligence</td>
                <td>Ms. Priya Patil</td>
            </tr>

            <tr>
                <td>2:00 PM</td>
                <td>Cloud Computing</td>
                <td>Mr. Amit Joshi</td>
            </tr>

        </table>

    </div>

    <!-- Contact Form -->

    <div class="container" id="contact">

        <h2><u>Contact Form</u></h2>

        <form>

            <p>
                <b>Name:</b><br>

                <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Enter your name">
            </p>

            <p>
                <b>Email:</b><br>

                <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Enter your email">
            </p>

            <p>
                <b>Message:</b><br>

                <textarea rows="4" placeholder="Enter your message"></textarea>
            </p>

            <p>
                <input type="submit" value="Send Message" class="btn">

                <input type="reset" value="Reset" class="btn">
            </p>

        </form>

    </div>

</body>
</html>
